<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-76-1246 </DOCNO><TEXT>As the expert system had become easy to structure, through the necessityto maintain the gas absorption cold/hot water unit and commercializationof expert shell package soft, an expert system to diagnose the gas absorptioncold/hot water unit was finally introduced and put to practical use byTokyo Gas. That system is utilized for not only the actual diagnosis,but also the utilization as an instructional tool for the service engineers.During the development, the computer was taken care of to be light andportable in use for the service tour of inspection, capable of describingin detail the explanatory scope to support the service engineers, andusable with the commercialized expert shell to heighten the developmentefficiency. By the simplified expert system of this time, a basic logicfor the diagnosis was made up. (7 figs, 2 tabs, 2 refs)</TEXT></DOC>